Prompt:
Ask me what language do I wish to translated from.
Ask me in what languages i wish to have transations in the category Translations, suggest me Polish, Spanish, English, German and Russian (with Polish transliteration for Russian).
I would like to get a detailed definition of a word in language. To do so, please include the following information in a table:

Definition in language: Provide a precise and concise definition of the word you are looking for, mentioning what it is and its use.
Translations: Provide translations of the word in the languages mentioned before. 
Examples of usage: Give an example of the use of the word in language.
Etymology: Indicate the origin of the word, specifying its evolution and its root if possible.
Pronunciation: Provide the IPA (International Phonetic Alphabet) and the simplified phonetic reading in language.
Key words must be in bold in the definition. Start directly with the table without preamble, and if the word is a conjugated verb, include the infinitive in the category "definition in language".
